ly from the Arabs. His son, also called Roger, ruled Sicily as king, presiding over a court noted for its splendour and patronage of the arts."],"variants":[{"name":"Rodger","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Roger  , in part from the surname derived from the given name in the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Roger Sibton was born about 1250, in Sibton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom as the son of Walter Sibton and Unknown. He had at least 1 son with Unknown."},"et":{"about 1250–":"umbes 1250–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1283–1340":"1283–1340","1230–Male":"1230–Surnud","about 1250":"umbes 1250","about 1283":"umbes 1283","1230":"1230","1340":"1340","1283":"1283","1250":"1250","Sibton, Suffolk, England":"Sibton, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1250–":"noin 1250–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1283–1340":"1283–1340","1230–Male":"1230–Kuollut","about 1250":"noin 1250","about 1283":"noin 1283","1230":"1230","1340":"1340","1283":"1283","1250":"1250","Sibton, Suffolk, England":"Sibton, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1250–":"environ 1250–Décédé","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1283–1340":"1283–1340","1230–Male":"1230–Décédé","about 1250":"environ 1250","about 1283":"environ 1283","1230":"1230","1340":"1340","1283":"1283","1250":"1250","Sibton, Suffolk, England":"Sibton, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Roger Sibton est né environ 1250, à Sibton, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Walter Sibton et Unknown. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Unknown."},"de":{"about 1250–":"um 1250–Verstorben","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1283–1340":"1283–1340","1230–Male":"1230–Verstorben","about 1250":"um 1250","about 1283":"um 1283","1230":"1230","1340":"1340","1283":"1283","1250":"1250","Sibton, Suffolk, England":"Sibton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Roger Sibton wurde um 1250 in Sibton, Suffolk, England, United King